  "texts": [
    "In marketing, sensorimotor experiences also play a key role in consumers' preferences for options (Kwon and Adaval 2018) and purchase intention (Elder and Krishna 2011).",
    "Findings from the field of sensory marketing further highlight that sensory experiences driven by physical stimuli and mental stimulation have an important impact on marketing outcomes (Krishna and Schwarz 2014).",
    "Influencers who use more sensory language in their content also attain more engagement and sales (Cascio Rizzo et al. 2023).",
    "Large language models (LLMs) do not own a physical body that is essential for sensory experiences.",
    "As a result, LLMs rely on vast volumes of training data to learn from those experiences."
  ],
